OL,3,CSoldier reflects on surviving knife
OL,4,Cattack metres from family home
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian in their
OL,7,Ffirst interview since the incident,
OL,8,FMark and his wife Eileen have
OL,9,Fdescribed the impact it's had on their
OL,10,Flives.
OL,12,F"For me it's really brought home knife
OL,13,Fcrime and the impact of knife crime,
OL,14,Fnot just on the victim but the wider
OL,15,Ffamily and community," Mark said.
OL,17,F"I'm definitely more aware of it on
OL,18,Fthe news, it's a realisation of how
OL,19,Ffortunate I was and we were."
