OL,6,F"It just speaks volumes as people were
OL,7,Finterested and invested in trying to
OL,8,Fmake sure that no one was coming to
OL,9,Fharm."
OL,11,FMark's wife, Eileen, was one of the
OL,12,Ffirst on the scene as he lay injured -
OL,13,Fand was trying to help, before she
OL,14,Feven realised the victim was in fact
OL,15,Fher own husband.
OL,17,F"We were in the garden having our
OL,18,Fdinner and I could hear something
OL,19,Foccurring, which then turned into a
OL,20,Fcall for police," Eileen said.
