OL,7,Fthings if someone's calling for
OL,8,Fpolice, I couldn't ignore that, so I
OL,9,Fdid get my phone and went out.
OL,11,F"And what I saw that was there was a
OL,12,Fsoldier lying on the ground.
OL,14,F"In my initial response, I was unaware
OL,15,Fit was my husband,"
