OL,6,FMark was initially approached by
OL,7,FAnthony Esan in the street - he asked
OL,8,Fif he could use Mark's phone because
OL,9,Fhis moped had broken down and he
OL,10,Fneeded to call someone to come and
OL,11,Fhelp - a lie the prosecution say he
OL,12,Fused to distract Mark.
OL,14,FDashcam footage was played in court
OL,15,Fshowing the attack in the middle of
OL,16,Fthe road with Esan stabbing Lt Col
OL,17,FTeeton, who gets up and walks the
OL,18,Fother way, and Esan going after him
OL,19,Fand continuing his attack.
