OL,6,FHe was treated in the intensive care
OL,7,Funit for a week before he began his
OL,8,Fslow recovery, starting with small
OL,9,Fwalks up and down the hospital
OL,10,Fcorridors.
OL,12,FAs Mark began his recovery he spent
OL,13,Ftwo weeks at home before receiving
OL,14,Ftreatment at the Defence
OL,15,FRehabilitation Centre.
OL,17,F"I really enjoyed my job, and I wanted
OL,18,Fto get back," he said.
OL,20,F"I wanted to get back to the family as
OL,21,Fwell.
