OL,3,CSoldier reflects on surviving knife
OL,4,Cattack metres from family home
OL,6,F"You only get through it if you've got
OL,7,Fthat support behind you.
OL,9,F"I only hope that, if anyone else is
OL,10,Fin slightly challenging times we can
OL,11,Fbe there for them."
OL,13,F"It has been an emotional
OL,14,Frollercoaster," Eileen added. "Just
OL,15,Fthe most horrific ordeal.
OL,17,F"But it's about the impact beyond just
OL,18,Fus - the stresses that you walk around
OL,19,Fwith on a daily basis, the stresses
OL,20,Four children are burdened with.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/11
