OL,3,CSoldier reflects on surviving knife
OL,4,Cattack metres from family home
OL,6,F"They amaze us in terms of how
OL,7,Fresilient and how well they've handled
OL,8,Fall of this.
OL,10,F"Our whole approach to life has
OL,11,Fchanged. It's just the need to be so
OL,12,Fgrateful for what we have, enjoy the
OL,13,Fsmall things, live every day as well
OL,14,Fas we can."
OL,16,FA Gofundme page has raised almost
OL,17,F#50,000 to support Lt Col Teeton and
OL,18,Fhis family.
